com.guidewire.ab.external.entity

Interface WorkflowStepStats

  • All Superinterfaces:
    gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity
    Deprecated. 
    External entities are deprecated. Please use the new Java API instead.

    @Deprecated
public interface WorkflowStepStats
extends gw.pl.external.entity.Entity, gw.pl.external.entity.KeyableEntity
    Workflow elapsed and execution time statistics aggregated by workflow step. Elapsed time is the total time spent from step entry to completion. Execution time is time spent on processing, excluding time spent waiting on triggers, activities, or timeouts.
